      "value": "<p>You can expend one @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.GHzO3cGJBSbXJdeF]{Superiority Die} and use a bonus action on your turn to feint, choosing one creature within 5 feet of you as your target. You have <strong>advantage </strong>on your next attack roll against that creature this turn. If that attack hits, add the superiority die to the attack's damage roll.</p><section id=\"secret-lMFCQOPC5Yr3VVLD\" class=\"secret\"><p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">Note: After adding this feature to your character, edit this feature's details and set Resource Consumption to Items Uses: Combat Superiority.</em></p></section>",
